{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":552,"text":"Dre Urhahn: This theater \nis built on Copacabana,"},{"time":3380,"text":"which is the most famous \nbeach in the world,"},{"time":6483,"text":"but 25 kilometers away from here"},{"time":8281,"text":"in the North Zone of Rio"},{"time":10297,"text":"lies a community called Vila Cruzeiro,"},{"time":13359,"text":"and roughly 60,000 people live there."},{"time":16419,"text":"Now, the people here in Rio mostly know"},{"time":18522,"text":"Vila Cruzeiro from the news,"},{"time":20397,"text":"and unfortunately, news \nfrom Vila Cruzeiro often"},{"time":24034,"text":"is not good news."},{"time":26466,"text":"But Vila Cruzeiro is also the place"},{"time":29367,"text":"where our story begins."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31392,"text":"Jeroen Koolhaas: Ten years \nago, we first came to Rio"},{"time":34165,"text":"to shoot a documentary \nabout life in the favelas."},{"time":37792,"text":"Now, we learned that favelas \nare informal communities."},{"time":40694,"text":"They emerged over the years"},{"time":41911,"text":"when immigrants from the countryside"},{"time":43771,"text":"came to the cities looking for work,"},{"time":45783,"text":"like cities within the cities,"},{"time":48029,"text":"known for problems like crime, poverty,"},{"time":50595,"text":"and the violent drug war between"},{"time":52356,"text":"police and the drug gangs."},{"time":53768,"text":"So what struck us was that"},{"time":57013,"text":"these were communities that the people"},{"time":58570,"text":"who lived there had built \nwith their own hands,"},{"time":61050,"text":"without a master plan"},{"time":62600,"text":"and like a giant work in progress."},{"time":65500,"text":"Where we're from, in Holland,"},{"time":67374,"text":"everything is planned."},{"time":69457,"text":"We even have rules for \nhow to follow the rules."},{"time":72121,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":73677,"text":"DU: So the last day of \nfilming, we ended up"},{"time":75795,"text":"in Vila Cruzeiro, and \nwe were sitting down"},{"time":77944,"text":"and we had a drink,"},{"time":79332,"text":"and we were overlooking this hill"},{"time":81007,"text":"with all these houses,"},{"time":82617,"text":"and most of these houses looked unfinished,"},{"time":84952,"text":"and they had walls of bare brick,"},{"time":86382,"text":"but we saw some of these houses"},{"time":88132,"text":"which were plastered and painted,"},{"time":90074,"text":"and suddenly we had this idea:"},{"time":91770,"text":"what would it look like if all these houses"},{"time":94450,"text":"would be plastered and painted?"},{"time":96625,"text":"And then we imagined one big design,"},{"time":99667,"text":"one big work of art."},{"time":102767,"text":"Who would expect something like that"},{"time":104423,"text":"in a place like this?"},{"time":106289,"text":"So we thought, would that even be possible?"},{"time":109452,"text":"So first we started to count the houses,"},{"time":112140,"text":"but we soon lost count."},{"time":114038,"text":"But somehow the idea stuck."}]},{"cues":[{"time":117234,"text":"JK: We had a friend."},{"time":118909,"text":"He ran an NGO in Vila Cruzeiro."},{"time":121520,"text":"His name was Nanko,"},{"time":122805,"text":"and he also liked the idea."},{"time":124866,"text":"He said, \"You know, everybody here"},{"time":126538,"text":"would pretty much love \nto have their houses"},{"time":128411,"text":"plastered and painted."},{"time":129862,"text":"It's when a house is finished.\""},{"time":132097,"text":"So he introduced us to the right people,"},{"time":134066,"text":"and Vitor and Maurinho became our crew."},{"time":137097,"text":"We picked three houses in\nthe center of the community"},{"time":140014,"text":"and we start here. We made a few designs,"},{"time":142494,"text":"and everybody liked this design"},{"time":144114,"text":"of a boy flying a kite the best."},{"time":146527,"text":"So we started painting, \nand the first thing we did"},{"time":148668,"text":"was to paint everything blue,"},{"time":151059,"text":"and we thought that looked \nalready pretty good."},{"time":153650,"text":"But they hated it. The people\nwho lived there really hated it."},{"time":156181,"text":"They said, \"What did you do?"},{"time":157824,"text":"You painted our house in \nexactly the same color"},{"time":159713,"text":"as the police station.\""},{"time":161513,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":163426,"text":"In a favela, that is not a good thing."},{"time":165652,"text":"Also the same color as the prison cell."},{"time":169477,"text":"So we quickly went ahead \nand we painted the boy,"},{"time":172931,"text":"and then we thought we were finished,"},{"time":174139,"text":"we were really happy, but still,"},{"time":176676,"text":"it wasn't good because the little\nkids started coming up to us,"},{"time":179069,"text":"and they said, \"You know, \nthere's a boy flying the kite,"},{"time":181131,"text":"but where is his kite?\""},{"time":183178,"text":"We said, \"Uh, it's art."},{"time":185293,"text":"You know, you have to imagine the kite.\""},{"time":187810,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":188862,"text":"And they said, \"No, no, no, \nwe want to see the kite.\""},{"time":192526,"text":"So we quickly installed a kite"},{"time":194423,"text":"way up high on the hill,"},{"time":195788,"text":"so that you could see \nthe boy flying the kite"},{"time":197920,"text":"and you could actually see a kite."},{"time":200333,"text":"So the local news started writing about it,"},{"time":202188,"text":"which was great,"},{"time":203501,"text":"and then even The Guardian wrote about it:"},{"time":205088,"text":"\"Notorious slum becomes open-air gallery.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":209264,"text":"JK: So, encouraged by this success,"},{"time":212182,"text":"we went back to Rio for a second project,"},{"time":215710,"text":"and we stumbled upon this street."},{"time":218336,"text":"It was covered in concrete \nto prevent mudslides,"},{"time":221609,"text":"and somehow we saw a sort of river in it,"},{"time":224960,"text":"and we imagined this river\nto be a river in Japanese style"},{"time":228444,"text":"with koi carp swimming upstream."},{"time":231190,"text":"So we decided to paint that river,"},{"time":233291,"text":"and we invited Rob Admiraal,"},{"time":235913,"text":"who is a tattoo artist,"},{"time":237313,"text":"and he specialized in the Japanese style."},{"time":240333,"text":"So little did we know that we would spend"},{"time":242020,"text":"almost an entire year painting that river,"},{"time":245455,"text":"together with Geovani\nand Robinho and Vitor,"},{"time":249175,"text":"who lived nearby."},{"time":251301,"text":"And we even moved into the neighborhood"},{"time":253371,"text":"when one of the guys that \nlived on the street, Elias,"},{"time":256734,"text":"told us that we could come \nand live in his house,"},{"time":259659,"text":"together with his family,"},{"time":261007,"text":"which was fantastic."},{"time":262477,"text":"Unfortunately, during that time,"},{"time":263805,"text":"another war broke out between the police"},{"time":266086,"text":"and the drug gangs."},{"time":267861,"text":"(Video) (Gunfire)"},{"time":282218,"text":"We learned that during those times,"},{"time":285124,"text":"people in communities \nreally stick together"},{"time":287494,"text":"during these times of hardship,"},{"time":289282,"text":"but we also learned a \nvery important element,"},{"time":291892,"text":"the importance of barbecues. \n(Laughter)"},{"time":295199,"text":"Because, when you throw a barbecue,"},{"time":296920,"text":"it turns you from a guest into a host,"},{"time":299361,"text":"so we decided to throw one"},{"time":300574,"text":"almost every other week,"},{"time":301797,"text":"and we got to know everybody \nin the neighborhood."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304806,"text":"JK: We still had this \nidea of the hill, though."}]},{"cues":[{"time":306831,"text":"DU: Yeah, yeah, we were talking about"},{"time":308191,"text":"the scale of this, because this painting"},{"time":310137,"text":"was incredibly big,"},{"time":312398,"text":"and it was insanely detailed,"},{"time":314546,"text":"and this process almost drove\nus completely insane ourselves."},{"time":320285,"text":"But we figured that maybe, \nduring this process,"},{"time":323480,"text":"all the time that we had \nspent in the neighborhood"},{"time":325651,"text":"was maybe actually even more important"},{"time":327225,"text":"than the painting itself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":329926,"text":"JK: So after all that time,"},{"time":331444,"text":"this hill, this idea was still there,"},{"time":333873,"text":"and we started to make sketches,"},{"time":336258,"text":"models, and we figured something out."},{"time":339442,"text":"We figured that our ideas, our designs"},{"time":341545,"text":"had to be a little bit more simple than that last project"},{"time":345314,"text":"so that we could paint with more people"},{"time":347458,"text":"and cover more houses at the same time."},{"time":351114,"text":"And we had an opportunity to try that out"},{"time":353470,"text":"in a community in the central part of Rio,"},{"time":356040,"text":"which is called Santa Marta,"},{"time":357788,"text":"and we made a design for this place"},{"time":359971,"text":"which looked like this,"},{"time":361362,"text":"and then we got people to go along with it"},{"time":362907,"text":"because turns out that if \nyour idea is ridiculously big,"},{"time":366930,"text":"it's easier to get people to \ngo along with this. (Laughter)"},{"time":370500,"text":"And the people of Santa Marta"},{"time":373468,"text":"got together and in a little over a month"},{"time":376216,"text":"they turned that square into this."},{"time":378589,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":385676,"text":"And this image somehow \nwent all over the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":388870,"text":"DU: So then we received \nan unexpected phone call"},{"time":392638,"text":"from the Philadelphia Mural Arts Program,"},{"time":396305,"text":"and they had this question"},{"time":397880,"text":"if this idea, our approach,"},{"time":399781,"text":"if this would actually \nwork in North Philly,"},{"time":402695,"text":"which is one of the poorest neighborhoods"},{"time":405126,"text":"in the United States."},{"time":406778,"text":"So we immediately said yes."},{"time":409838,"text":"We had no idea how,"},{"time":411748,"text":"but it seemed like a very \ninteresting challenge,"},{"time":414169,"text":"so we did exactly the \nsame as we did in Rio,"},{"time":416430,"text":"and we moved into the neighborhood"},{"time":418101,"text":"and started barbecuing."},{"time":420243,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":425102,"text":"So the project took almost two years to complete,"},{"time":428871,"text":"and we made individual designs"},{"time":430761,"text":"for every single house on \nthe avenue that we painted,"},{"time":433304,"text":"and we made these designs together"},{"time":434908,"text":"with the local store owners, \nthe building owners,"},{"time":437521,"text":"and a team of about a dozen \nyoung men and women."},{"time":442459,"text":"They were hired, and then\nthey were trained as painters,"},{"time":445958,"text":"and together they transformed\ntheir own neighborhood,"},{"time":449523,"text":"the whole street, into a \ngiant patchwork of color."},{"time":454340,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":460142,"text":"And at the end, the city of Philadelphia"},{"time":463765,"text":"thanked every single one of them"},{"time":465778,"text":"and gave them a merit for\ntheir accomplishment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":469094,"text":"JK: So now we had painted a whole street."},{"time":472246,"text":"How about we do this whole hill now?"},{"time":475801,"text":"We started looking for funding,"},{"time":477679,"text":"but instead, we just ran into questions,"},{"time":480920,"text":"like, how many houses \nare you going to paint?"},{"time":484339,"text":"How many square meters is that?"},{"time":486495,"text":"How much paint are you going to use,"},{"time":488546,"text":"and how many people are you going to employ?"},{"time":491189,"text":"And we did try for years to write plans"},{"time":493900,"text":"for the funding and answer \nall those questions,"},{"time":497219,"text":"but then we thought,"},{"time":498759,"text":"in order to answer all those questions,"},{"time":500672,"text":"you have to know exactly \nwhat you're going to do"},{"time":503259,"text":"before you actually get there and start."},{"time":506443,"text":"And maybe it's a mistake \nto think like that."},{"time":509694,"text":"It would lose some of the \nmagic that we had learned"},{"time":512222,"text":"about that if you go somewhere"},{"time":513848,"text":"and you spend time there,"},{"time":516263,"text":"you can let the project grow organically"},{"time":518231,"text":"and have a life of its own."}]},{"cues":[{"time":521719,"text":"DU: So what we did is"},{"time":523931,"text":"we decided to take this \nplan and strip it away"},{"time":527140,"text":"from all the numbers"},{"time":529030,"text":"and all the ideas and presumptions"},{"time":530999,"text":"and just go back to the base idea,"},{"time":533362,"text":"which was to transform this hill"},{"time":535364,"text":"into a giant work of art."},{"time":537805,"text":"And instead of looking for funding,"},{"time":540207,"text":"we started a crowdfunding campaign,"},{"time":543097,"text":"and in a little over a month,"},{"time":544680,"text":"more than 1,500 people put together"},{"time":546852,"text":"and donated over 100,000 dollars."},{"time":550127,"text":"So for us, this was an amazing \nmoment, because now —"},{"time":553730,"text":"(Applause) —"},{"time":557246,"text":"because now we finally had the freedom"},{"time":560295,"text":"to use all the lessons that we had learned"},{"time":562466,"text":"and create a project that was built"},{"time":565562,"text":"the same way that the favela was built,"},{"time":567474,"text":"from the ground on up, bottom up,"},{"time":569128,"text":"with no master plan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":571703,"text":"JK: So we went back, \nand we employed Angelo,"},{"time":574800,"text":"and he's a local artist from Vila Cruzeiro,"},{"time":576722,"text":"very talented guy, and he\nknows almost everybody there,"},{"time":579518,"text":"and then we employed Elias, our former landlord"},{"time":581940,"text":"who invited us into his house,"},{"time":583537,"text":"and he's a master of construction."},{"time":585551,"text":"Together with them, we decided where to start."},{"time":587992,"text":"We picked this spot in Vila Cruzeiro,"},{"time":589678,"text":"and houses are being plastered as we speak."},{"time":592491,"text":"And the good thing about them is that"},{"time":594071,"text":"they are deciding which houses go next."},{"time":596066,"text":"They're even printing t-shirts,"},{"time":597752,"text":"they're putting up banners"},{"time":599318,"text":"explaining everything to everybody,"},{"time":601302,"text":"and talking to the press."},{"time":603143,"text":"This article about Angelo appeared."}]},{"cues":[{"time":605610,"text":"DU: So while this is happening,"},{"time":606788,"text":"we are bringing this \nidea all over the world."},{"time":608973,"text":"So, like the project we \ndid in Philadelphia,"},{"time":612290,"text":"we are also invited to do workshops,"},{"time":614438,"text":"for instance in Curaçao,"},{"time":616350,"text":"and right now we're planning \na huge project in Haiti."}]},{"cues":[{"time":620456,"text":"JK: So the favela was not only the place"},{"time":623200,"text":"where this idea started:"},{"time":624787,"text":"it was also the place that made it possible"},{"time":628342,"text":"to work without a master plan,"},{"time":631468,"text":"because these communities are informal —"},{"time":633538,"text":"this was the inspiration —"},{"time":634977,"text":"and in a communal effort, \ntogether with the people,"},{"time":637577,"text":"you can almost work like in an orchestra,"},{"time":639488,"text":"where you can have a hundred instruments"},{"time":641062,"text":"playing together to create a symphony."}]},{"cues":[{"time":643415,"text":"DU: So we want to thank everybody who"},{"time":645372,"text":"wanted to become part of this dream"},{"time":646990,"text":"and supported us along the way,"},{"time":649174,"text":"and we are looking at continuing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":651885,"text":"JK: Yeah. And so one day pretty soon,"},{"time":653696,"text":"when the colors start \ngoing up on these walls,"},{"time":656205,"text":"we hope more people will join us,"},{"time":658184,"text":"and join this big dream,"},{"time":660997,"text":"and maybe one day, the \nwhole of Vila Cruzeiro"},{"time":663617,"text":"will be painted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":665372,"text":"DU: Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":667284,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}